{"lemma":"أَصْفِياء","slug":"أَصْفِياء","root":"ص.ف.#","root_slug":"ص-ف-_","root_link":"/words/roots/ص-ف-_","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["verb"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":2},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n24547"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%A3%D9%8E%D8%B5%D9%92%D9%81%D9%90%D9%8A%D8%A7%D8%A1"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to purify, to liquidate"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to sort out, to clarify"}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":["/sˤaf.faː/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n24547","headword_ar":"صَفِىٌّ","root":"Sfw","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SaAfK","text_ar":"صَافٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":". ―         -b2-  Also (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A friend who regards one,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"behaves towards one, with reciprocal purity"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sincerity of love"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"affection,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of brotherly affection:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, * M, * K, TA:) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aSofiyaA='u","text_ar":"اَصْفِيَا=ءُ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.) One says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fulaAnN SafiY~u fulaAnK","text_ar":"فُلَانٌ صَفِىُّ فُلَانٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Such a man is the friend"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of such a man"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fulaAnapu SafiY~u fulaAnK","text_ar":"فُلَانَةُ صَفِىُّ فُلَانٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Safiy~atuhu","text_ar":"صَفِيَّتُهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Such a woman is the friend,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of such a man"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (Ham p. 430.) ―         -b3-  See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SafowN","text_ar":"صَفْوٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in two places. ―         -b4-  Also (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The portion, of the spoil, which the chief,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"commander, chooses for himself before the division;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Msb, K, TA;) and so ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Safiy~apN","text_ar":"صَفِيَّةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", of which the pl. is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SafaAyaA","text_ar":"صَفَايَا"},{"kind":"text","text":": (S, Msb:) or, accord. to As,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SafaAyaA","text_ar":"صَفَايَا"},{"kind":"text","text":"is pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SafiY~N","text_ar":"صَفِىٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", which signifies the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"portion which the chief chooses for himself, exclusively of his companions, such as the horse, and that which cannot be divided among the army:"},{"kind":"text","text":"or, as AO says, the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"portion which the chief chose for himself, after"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"taking"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the fourth part, such as the she-camel, and the horse, and the sword, and the girl"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"young woman;"},{"kind":"text","text":"and thus it continued to be in the case of El-Islám, but the fourth became reduced to the fifth. (Msb.) ―         -b5-  Also, applied to a she-camel, (S, M, K,) and to a ewe, or she-goat, (S,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Abounding with milk;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, M, K;) or so ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Safiy~apN","text_ar":"صَفِيَّةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (Z, TA:) or the former, a she-camel"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"whose milk lasts throughout the year:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(IAar, TA in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$kr","text_ar":"شكر"},{"kind":"text","text":":) pl. of the former, (Sb, S, M, K,) or of the latter, (Z, TA,) as above: (Sb, S, M, Z, K:) Sb says that it is not pluralized with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A","text_ar":"ا"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"t","text_ar":"ت"},{"kind":"text","text":"because the sing. is without"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"p","text_ar":"ة"},{"kind":"text","text":". (M.) ―         -b6-  And A palm-tree ("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"naxolapN","text_ar":"نَخْلَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":")"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"abounding with fruit;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, K;) or so ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Safiy~apN","text_ar":"صَفِيَّةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (Z, TA:) pl. of the former, (TA,) or of the latter, as above. (Z, TA.)"}],"source_refs":["S","Msb","M","K","Z","TA","Sb"]}]},"classical_definitions":{"source":"hawramani","url":"https://arabiclexicon.hawramani.com/%D8%B5%D9%81%D9%8A/","headword_ar":"صفي","entries":[{"lexicon_id":"dictionary_18","lexicon_en":"Al-Sharīf al-Jurjānī, Kitāb al-Taʿrīfāt (d. 1413 CE)","lexicon_ar":"كتاب التعريفات للشريف الجرجاني","permalink":"https://arabiclexicon.hawramani.com/?p=23364#78132d","body_html":"<span>الصفي: هو شيء نفيس كان يصطفيه النبي، صلى الله عليه وسلم، لنفسه، كسيف أو فرس أو أَمَةٍ.</span>"}]}}